('Gestoría Pérez del Albir', 'Tax/Accounting', 'Established gestoría and tax advisory firm with over 40 years of experience serving clients in the Albir and Costa Blanca region. Located in the heart of Albir, a popular area for UK expats and international residents. Comprehensive services include tax advisory and planning, accounting and bookkeeping, payroll management, vehicle transfers and registrations, inheritance and estate planning (non-resident tax services), property-related tax matters, and general Spanish administrative procedures. Licensed agents for Generali insurance. Professional team offering personalized service to individuals, freelancers, and small businesses. Experience working with non-residents and international clients navigating Spanish tax and administrative systems.', 'Avda. del Albir, 38, 03581 Albir - Alfaz del Pi', 'Albir', 'Alicante', '+34 966 865 356', 'info@gestoriaperez.com', 'https://www.gestoriaperez.com', true, false, false, false, NOW(), NOW());
